* Qing dynasty: Grand Secretariat → Grand Council → Cabinet
* Republic of China: State Council (1912–28) → Executive Yuan (1928–present)
* People&#x27;s Republic of China: Government Administration Council of the Central People&#x27;s Government (1949–54); Constituent departments of the PRC

