*&quot;Shepherd&#x27;s Idyll&quot; (1768), Metropolitan Museum of Art
*&quot;Washerwomen&quot; (1768), Metropolitan Museum of Art
*&quot;Jupiter and Callisto&quot; (1769), Wallace Collection, London
